        Return 0
    
    If k == 0 || k == n:
        Return 1
    
    Note: Use iterative computation to avoid large factorials
    Let result be 1
    Let i be 0
    
    While i < k:
        Set result to result * (n - i) / (i + 1)
        Set i to i + 1
    
    Return result

Process called "compute_symmetric_dimension" that takes n as Integer, k as Integer returns Integer:
